high_descs: Face the island counter on the right
Pick up the spoon with the  blue handle
Turn left and go to the sink on the left
Put spoon in the sink, turn on the sink and take the spoon out
Turn right and go to the far right cabinet under the counter
Open the cabinet door, put the spoon in front of the  salt and close the door
anns.task_desc: Wash spoon and put it in a cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the counter, then hang a right and walk up to the kitchen island.
Pick up the large golden spoon off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the golden spoon in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean golden spoon.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and take a couple steps forward then turn around to face the cabinets.
Open the lower right cabinet door and put the clean golden spoon inside the cabinet, then close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean golden spoon in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter, above the oven, on your right.
Pick up the ladle between the soap dispenser and the head of lettuce, on the counter top.
Turn to your left and go past the counter, then turn right to go around the counter, and turn to the sink on your left.
Place the ladle in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the ladle off, turn the water off, and remove the ladle from the sink.
Move over to the bottom cabinet, to the right of the dishwasher.
Place the ladle in the cabinet, in front of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle in the cabinet.
